title: Seamless Cartoon Textures
description: This unique set includes 20 high-quality, stylized cartoon textures that game developers can seamlessly integrate into their projects.
longDescription:
Introducing our dynamic Cartoon Texture Pack - a remarkable collection specifically designed to enrich the aesthetics of MOBA and Strategy games. This unique set includes 20 high-quality, stylized cartoon textures that game developers can seamlessly integrate into their projects.


But we didn't just stop at creating unique, eye-catching textures. This pack also features normal maps, offering the means to produce stunning, realistic lighting effects that give your environments a more three-dimensional look, enhancing both realism and immersion.


To further detail your environments, our collection also includes height maps, allowing you to create a more tangible and interactive world by adding depth and dimension to your surfaces. The illusion of rough, uneven, or complex surfaces can be easily achieved, adding another layer of realism to your gaming experiences.


Finally, the pack incorporates ambient occlusion maps. These are designed to simulate the way light radiates in real life, especially off what are normally considered non-reflective surfaces. This means your scenes will benefit from more realistic shading and an enhanced depth perception, providing a visually stunning and immersive environment for your players.


Technical Information:


20 Individual Diffuse PNG's

Maps Included: Height, Normal, Ambient Occlusion

Image sizes: 1024px by 1024px
